metadata.name: After half
metadata.description:
The doctor came out and asked, "Who's next of kin?"



Yang Yi rushed up, "I am, I am her father!"



"Prepare to sign to do an operation, still have, the operation cost hundred thousand, go to pay money now." The doctor said, and turned away.



"Doctor, what's wrong with my daughter? What's the matter?" Yang Yi asked after him.



The doctor was a little impatient. "Chronic malnutrition, multiple wounds on the body, and a tumor in the stomach. How on earth are you a father?"



Boom!
